---
title: Pizza Inspired Chicken and Chorizo Pasta Bake with Spinach and Garlic Ciabatta
description: Pasta bakes are a crowd-pleasing dish, typically pairing tomatoey sauces with gooey melted cheese. Here, we're adding chorizo for a pizza inspired dish, paired with garlic bread for a hearty meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R10_W47_UK_F14691-5_Main_low-4bfe3d73.jpg
